scenes.description: Mori Calliope and Rikka talk on stage after their performance of "Spiral Tones."
Mori Calliope delivers an MC segment, thanking Rikka, drinking water, and introducing the next song.
Performance of "The Grim Reaper is a Live-Streamer."
